parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Loss of Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power and stalling of the engine can lead to accidents, especially when driving at high speeds or navigating through intersections. The loss of power steering and brakes can make it difficult to control the vehicle, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls or shuts off while driving
often without warning
resulting in a loss of power steering and brakes.
